    slug: `caption-phone-setup`,
    title: `Captioned Telephone (CapTel/Caption Call): Make Phone Calls Easier With Live Captions`,
    excerpt: `Captioned phones show a real-time text transcript of what the other person is saying during a call — a free service available to people with hearing loss.`,
